and it's less sad

300
00:38:07.820 --> 00:38:09.452
if there's another person
with me.

301
00:38:09.654 --> 00:38:11.052
-Yeah. Sure.
-Yeah?

302
00:38:11.088 --> 00:38:12.454
Sure. Yeah.
That sounds nice.

303
00:38:12.489 --> 00:38:13.530
