stayed out longer.

306
00:38:33.987 --> 00:38:35.915
I look radiant with vodka.

307
00:38:42.026 --> 00:38:43.362
Do you like port?

308
00:38:43.862 --> 00:38:45.056
Yeah. Sure.

309
00:38:49.529 --> 00:38:50.658
